#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about family budgets.\n"
"\n"
"Many families are stressed about money, especially if teens keep asking for things!\n"
"\n"
"When we make a budget together, we can agree how to spend AND save to prevent stress and work towards our familyâ€™s goals."
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo inahusu bajeti za familia.\n"
"\n"
"Familia nyingi hufadhaika kuhusu pesa, hasa ikiwa vijana wanaendelea kuomba vitu!\n"
"\n"
"Tunapopanga bajeti pamoja, tunaweza kukubaliana jinsi ya kutumia na kuweka akiba ili kuzuia mfadhaiko na kufanyia kazi malengo ya familia yetu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is family budgeting.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to create a budget, but it is even more important to create a budget involving the entire family.\n"
"\n"
"Doing it together helps increase the level of understanding of how you spend money as a family and how much you save for the family and you can even come up with plans of how you can save as a family."
msgstr ""
"Habari, zenu.\n"
"\n"
"Mada ya leo ni kuhusu bajeti za familia.\n"
"\n"
"Ni muhimu kupanga bajeti, lakini ni muhimu zaidi kupanga bajeti inayohusisha familia nzima.\n"
"\n"
"Kufanya hivyo pamoja kunasaidia kuongeza kiwango cha uelewa wa jinsi mnavyotumia pesa kama familia na kiasi gani mnaweka akiba kwa ajili ya familia na mnaweza hata kupanga mipango ya jinsi mnavyoweza kuweka akiba mkiwa kama familia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When we involve our teens in budgeting, they learn to be responsible with money and work towards goals. That is something we all want for our teens, right?"
msgstr "Tunapowashirikisha vijana wetu katika kupanga bajeti, wanajifunza kuwajibika na pesa na kufanya kazi kwa malengo. Hilo ni jambo ambalo sote tunataka kwa vijana wetu, sivyo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_6.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_female_6.name involved her teens in budgeting"
msgstr "Sikiliza jinsi @data.characters.media_female_6.name alivyowashirikisha vijana wake katika kupanga bajeti"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Saving and budgeting helps me as a parent, and it helps my teens as well to understand where the money goes.\n"
"\n"
"My teens always asked for a lot of things and they did not understand when I said â€œI do not have money.â€ They would say â€œbut you have a job!â€\n"
"\n"
"I sat down with them and showed them all the things we pay for and how much is left. They understand now and even give ideas on how we can save to work towards our goals like new shoes or a birthday and bigger goals like their school fees. For the older one, I even opened a savings account."
msgstr ""
"Kuweka akiba na kupanga bajeti hunisaidia kama mzazi, na huwasaidia vijana wangu pia kuelewa pesa ziendako.\n"
"\n"
"Vijana wangu sikuzote waliomba vitu vingi na hawakuelewa niliposema â€œSina pesa.â€ Wangesema \"lakini unayo kazi!\"\n"
"\n"
"Nilikaa nao na kuwaonyesha vitu vyote tunavyolipia na ni kiasi gani kilichobaki. Wanaelewa sasa na hata kutoa mawazo kuhusu jinsi tunavyoweza kuweka akiba ili kufanyia kazi malengo yetu kama vile viatu vipya au siku ya kuzaliwa na malengo makubwa zaidi kama vile ada zao za shule. Kwa yule mkubwa, hata nilifungua akaunti ya akiba."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It can be hard to make ends meet every month. Many families have this problem!\n"
"\n"
"Including @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name â€“ let's have a look:"
msgstr ""
"Inaweza kuwa vigumu kupata riziki kila mwezi. Familia nyingi zina shida hii!\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwa ni pamoja na @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name - hebu tuangalie:"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I have been taking care of my grandchildren, @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name and @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, since their parents died when they were young. We often struggle with money, as I only receive a small grant."
msgstr "Nimekuwa nikiwatunza wajukuu zangu, @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name na @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, tangu wazazi wao wafariki walipokuwa wadogo. Mara nyingi tunahangaika na pesa, kwani mimi hupokea ruzuku ndogo tu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am so stressed. I donâ€™t have any money left. And now I am fighting with my teens over things they want â€“ again."
msgstr "Nina mfadhaiko sana. Sina pesa yoyote iliyobaki. Na ninapigana na vijana wangu juu ya mambo wanayotaka - tena."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name's
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Dealing with money challenges, like @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name's situation, is stressful. \n"
"\n"
"A family budget can help @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name - and YOU!"
msgstr ""
"Kukabiliana na changamoto za pesa, kama hali ya @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name's ni ya kufadhaisha.\n"
"\n"
"Bajeti ya familia inaweza kusaidia @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name - na WEWE!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**There are four steps for doing a family budget:**\n"
"\n"
"ğŸ’­ Step 1: THINK \n"
"ğŸ¯ Step 2: CHOOSE \n"
"âš’ï¸  Step 3: BUILD \n"
"ğŸ“‹ Step 4: PLAN"
msgstr ""
"**Kuna hatua nne za kupanga bajeti ya familia:**\n"
"\n"
"ğŸ’­ Hatua 1: FIKIRIA\n"
"ğŸ¯ Hatua 2: CHAGUA\n"
"âš’ï¸  Hatua 3: JENGA\n"
"ğŸ“‹ Hatua 4: PANGA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you complete these steps together with your family now?"
msgstr "Unaweza kukamilisha hatua hizi pamoja na familia yako sasa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My family can join in now"
msgstr "Familia yangu inaweza kujiunga sasa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let me try it out by myself"
msgstr "Ngoja niijaribu peke yangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You need:\n"
"\n"
"- ğŸ““Papers (or old newspaper or a cardboard box) and pens\n"
"- ğŸ«˜ Stones or beans or anything with lots of bits to represent money\n"
"\n"
"Take a minute to get these things before we start with the first step."
msgstr ""
"Unahitaji:\n"
"\n"
"- ğŸ““ Karatasi (au gazeti la zamani au kasha la karatasi nene) na kalamu\n"
"- ğŸ«˜ Hindi au maharage au kitu chochote chenye chembechembe nyingi kitakachowakilisha pesa\n"
"\n"
"Tumia dakika moja kutafuta vitu hivyo kabla hatujaanza hatua ya kwanza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Step 1: THINK**\n"
"Think about what you spend money on each month."
msgstr ""
"**Hatua ya 1: FIKIRI**\n"
"Fikiria juu ya kile unachotumia pesa kila mwezi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"- Draw pictures of all the things that you and your family spend money on each month.\n"
"- Write next to each picture how much each thing costs each month (there is no need to share the numbers if you donâ€™t want to).\n"
"- Add up how much money you have to spend each month."
msgstr ""
"- Chora picha za vitu vyote ambavyo wewe na familia yako mnatumia pesa kila mwezi.\n"
"- Andika karibu na kila picha ni kiasi gani kila kitu kinagharimu kila mwezi (hakuna haja ya kushirikisha namba ikiwa hutaki).\n"
"- Ongeza kiasi cha pesa unachopaswa kutumia kila mwezi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Step 2: CHOOSE**\n"
"Think about your needs and wants.\n"
"- WANT is something you can live without. \n"
"- NEED is something you cannot live without."
msgstr ""
"**Hatua ya 2: CHAGUA**\n"
"Fikiria juu ya mahitaji na matakwa yako.\n"
"- KUTAKA ni kitu ambacho unaweza kuishi bila kuwa nacho. \n"
"- UHITAJI ni kitu ambacho huwezi kuishi bila kuwa nacho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Look at your list of things you spend money on and choose:\n"
"\n"
"- Which are NEEDS that you cannot live without? Why?\n"
"- Which are WANTS which are nice to have but not essential? Why?\n"
"- Which things could you try to spend less money on?"
msgstr ""
"Angalia orodha yako ya vitu unavyotumia pesa na uchague:\n"
"\n"
"- Je, ni MAHITAJI gani ambayo huwezi kuishi bila kuwa nayo? Kwa nini?\n"
"- Je, ni MATAMANIO yapi ambayo ni mazuri kuwa nayo lakini sio muhimu? Kwa nini?\n"
"- Ni mambo gani unaweza kujaribu kutumia pesa kidogo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Step 3: BUILD**\n"
"Make a budget!"
msgstr ""
"**Hatua ya 3: JENGA**\n"
"Tengeneza bajeti!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"- Write down what your income is for the month.\n"
"- Take some stones or beans or anything with lots of bits - this is your income for the month. For example: If your income is TSh2000 and you have 20 beans, each bean is TSh100.\n"
"- Decide what you will spend on, and put the stones/objects on that image.\n"
"\n"
"Not sure about your decisions? Having trouble deciding between \"needs\" and \"wants\"? Thatâ€™s totally fine! This exercise will get easier with practice."
msgstr ""
"- Andika mapato yako kwa mwezi.\n"
"- Chukua mawe au maharagwe au kitu chochote chenye punje nyingi - haya ni mapato yako ya mwezi. Kwa mfano: Ikiwa mapato yako ni TSh2000 na una maharage 20, kila maharagwe ni TSh100.\n"
"- Amua utatumia nini, na uweke mawe/vitu kwenye picha hiyo.\n"
"\n"
"Je, hauna uhakika na maamuzi yako? Je, unapata shida kuamua kati ya \"mahitaji\" na \"matamanio\"? Hiyo ni sawa kabisa! Zoezi hili litakuwa rahisi kwa kufanya mazoezi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Step 4: PLAN**\n"
"Plan how you can save money, so you can deal with emergencies and realise your family goals!"
msgstr ""
"**Hatua ya 4: PANGA**\n"
"Panga jinsi unavyoweza kuokoa pesa, ili uweze kukabiliana na dharura na kutambua malengo ya familia yako!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"If you can save even a tiny amount for the future or emergency - it can make a big difference over time.\n"
"\n"
"- Add a circle called â€œemergenciesâ€.\n"
"- Add a circle called â€œfamily goalsâ€.\n"
"- Now try to move your money around so you can save a bit every month for goals and emergencies."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa unaweza kutunza hata kiasi kidogo kwa siku zijazo au dharura - inaweza kuleta mabadiliko makubwa baada ya muda.\n"
"\n"
"- Ongeza mduara unaoitwa \"dharura\".\n"
"- Ongeza mduara unaoitwa \"malengo ya familia\".\n"
"- Sasa jaribu kusogeza pesa zako ili uweze kuweka akiba kila mwezi kwa malengo na dharura."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"CONGRATULATIONS!!! ğŸ‰ \n"
"\n"
"You have made your budget! Remember to do this exercise again with your other family members - if you agree on a plan together it will make a huge difference!\n"
"\n"
"Now, let's see how @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name made a plan with her money, just like you are doing:"
msgstr ""
"HONGERA SANA!!! ğŸ‰ \n"
"\n"
"Umetengeneza bajeti yako! Kumbuka kufanya zoezi hili tena na wanafamilia wako wengine - ikiwa mtakubaliana juu ya mpango pamoja italeta mabadiliko makubwa!\n"
"\n"
"Sasa, hebu tuone jinsi @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name alivyofanya mpango na pesa zake, kama vile unavyofanya:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I want the best future for my grandchildren, but I do not know where to get the money. Loan sharks are dangerous and paying them back is so expensive.\n"
"\n"
"I should save, but that feels impossible!"
msgstr ""
"Nawatakia wajukuu zangu mustakabali mwema, lakini sijui nitapata wapi pesa. Mambo ya mkopo ni hatari na kuwalipa ni gharama sana.\n"
"\n"
"Ninatakiwa kutunza, lakini ninahisi hiyo haiwezekani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My goal is to make sure my grandson can go to high school and my granddaughter can reach her dream of university. How can I save a lot of money with the little money I have?"
msgstr "Lengo langu ni kuhakikisha mjukuu wangu wa kiume anaweza kwenda shule na mjukuu wangu wa kike anaweza kufikia ndoto yake ya chuo kikuu. Je, ninawezaje kuokoa pesa nyingi kwa pesa kidogo niliyo nayo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I know â€“ letâ€™s start with a plan! First, let me make a budget â€“ a plan for how I can save my money. Then I will save just a little bit of money at a time â€“ I will even join a stokvel."
msgstr "Najua - hebu tuanze na mpango! Kwanza, acha nitengeneze bajeti - mpango wa jinsi ninavyoweza kutunza pesa zangu. Kisha nitatunza pesa kidogo tu kwa wakati - hata nitajiunga na mfuko wa kuweka akiba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I should also speak with my grandchildren to choose things that we can spend just a little bit less on each week. They will help me think of things we want but do not need."
msgstr "Ninapaswa pia kuzungumza na wajukuu zangu ili kuchagua vitu ambavyo tunaweza kutumia fedha kidogo tu kwa kila wiki. Watanisaidia kufikiria vitu tunavyo vitamani lakini hatuvihitaji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(A few years later)*"
msgstr "*(Miaka michache baadae)*"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.nameâ€™s
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.nameâ€™s
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look, we reached our dreams! I did not borrow any money from friends or loan sharks. By saving a tiny bit each week, I managed to pay for @data.characters.f2_son_15.nameâ€™s high school and save some money for @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.nameâ€™s university. I am so proud of this."
msgstr "Angalia, tumefikia ndoto zetu! Sikukopa pesa yoyote kutoka kwa marafiki au mikopo yenye riba kubwa. Kwa kuokoa pesa kidogo kila wiki, nilifanikiwa kulipia shule, kidato cha tano na cha sita ya @data.characters.f2_son_15.name na kuweka akiba kwa ajili ya chuo kikuu cha @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name. Ninajivunia sana hii."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Saving is important for one more reason - emergencies! @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name also learnt this along the way:"
msgstr "Kuweka akiba  ni muhimu kwa sababu moja zaidi - dharura! @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name pia alijifunza hili njiani:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One night there was a horrible storm that broke my roof. Everything was flooded. I suddenly had to find money to fix the roof. I just felt defeated."
msgstr "Usiku mmoja kulikuwa na dhoruba ya kutisha ambayo ilivunja paa yangu. Kila kitu kiliharibika. Ghafla nililazimika kutafuta pesa za kurekebisha paa. Nilihisi tu kushindwa."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Having a savings plan could have helped @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name to be prepared for this kind of emergency! \n"
"\n"
"There are different ways we can save: at home, by buying things we can sell for profit, at a bank, or in a stokvel.\n"
"\n"
"Think of the advantages and disadvantages of each savings option."
msgstr ""
"Kuwa na mpango wa kuweka akiba kungemsaidia @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name kuwa tayari kwa aina hii ya dharura.\n"
"\n"
"Kuna njia tofauti tunaweza kuweka akiba: nyumbani, kwa kununua vitu tunaweza kuuza kwa faida, katika benki, au vikundi vya akiba.\n"
"\n"
"Fikiria faida na hasara za kila chaguo la kuweka akiba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What is the best way your family can save?"
msgstr "Je, ni njia gani bora ambayo familia yako inaweza kuweka akiba ya fedha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Save money at home"
msgstr "Kutunza pesa nyumbani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Buy things you can sell for profit"
msgstr "Kununua vitu mnaweza kuviuza kwa faida"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Save money at a bank"
msgstr "Kutunza pesa katika benki"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Save in a stokvel/savings group"
msgstr "Kutunza kwenye stockvel/vikundi vya akiba"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whatever savings plan you choose, it will really help your family move forward!"
msgstr "Njia yoyote ya kujiwekea akiba mtakayoichagua itaisaidia sana familia yenu kusonga mbele!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We all have dreams for our family, just like @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name. By setting aside a bit of money every month, you can realise them too!\n"
"\n"
"Letâ€™s come up with some ideas for savings goals for you to make a budget plan."
msgstr "Sote tuna ndoto kwa ajili ya familia zetu, kama vile @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name. Kwa kutenga pesa kidogo kila mwezi, tunaweza kuzitambua pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What are your family savings goals?"
msgstr "Je, malengo ya familia yako ya kuweka akiba ni yapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teens completing school/university"
msgstr "Vijana kumaliza shule/chuo kikuu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Building / expanding a house for my family"
msgstr "Kujenga / kupanua nyumba kwa ajili ya familia yangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Starting a business"
msgstr "Kuanzisha biashara"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Buying a car for my family"
msgstr "Kununua gari ya familia yangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Such a great goal!\n"
"\n"
"By making a good budget and saving plan, you can achieve it and feel proud of yourself!"
msgstr ""
"Lengo kubwa kama hilo!\n"
"\n"
"Kwa kufanya bajeti nzuri na mpango wa kutunza, unaweza kufikia na kujivunia mwenyewe!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are this weekâ€™s takeaway skills to help you budget and save!"
msgstr "Huu hapa ni ujuzi wa kuchukua wa wiki hii ili kukusaidia kupanga bajeti na kuweka akiba!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STEP 1: THINK"
msgstr "HATUA YA 1: FIKIRIA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What do we spend on now?"
msgstr "Kwa sasa tunatumia pesa kwenye mambo gani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Write down or draw what you spend money on as a family each month. \n"
"\n"
"How much does each item cost? \n"
"How much money do you need in total?"
msgstr ""
"Andika au chora kile unachotumia pesa kama familia kila mwezi. \n"
"\n"
"Je, kila kitu kinagharimu kiasi gani? \n"
"Unahitaji pesa ngapi kiasi gani jumla?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STEP 2: CHOOSE"
msgstr "HATUA YA 2: CHAGUA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk together about needs and wants."
msgstr "Zungumzeni pamoja kuhusu mahitaji na matamanio."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Which expenses are a â€˜needâ€™ that you cannot live without? \n"
"Which expenses are a â€˜wantâ€™ that is nice to have but not essential? \n"
"Which things could you try to spend less on? \n"
"\n"
"When we explain and listen to each other carefully, we can make good money choices together as a family."
msgstr ""
"Ni gharama zipi ni â€˜hajaâ€™ ambayo huwezi kuishi bila kuwanazo? \n"
"Ni gharama zipi ni â€˜tamanioiâ€™ ambapo ni vizuri kuwa nacho lakini sio muhimu? \n"
"Ni vitu gani unaweza kujaribu kutumia kidogo? \n"
"\n"
"Tunapoelezana na kusikilizana kwa makini, tunaweza kufanya uchaguzi mzuri wa pesa pamoja kama familia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STEP 3: BUILD"
msgstr "HATUA YA 3: JENGA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make your own budget."
msgstr "Tengeneza bajeti yako mwenyewe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Write down your income for the month. \n"
"Take stones, beans, or anything with lots of bits - this is your income. \n"
"Agree how much you will spend on each item, and put the objects on that image/word."
msgstr ""
"Andika mapato yako kwa mwezi. \n"
"Chukua mawe, maharage, au kitu chochote kilicho na vipande vingi - haya ni mapato yako. \n"
"Kubali ni kiasi gani utatumia kwa kila kitu, na uweke vitu kwenye picha/neno hilo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STEP 4: PLAN"
msgstr "HATUA YA 4: PANGA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Plan for emergencies and family goals."
msgstr "Panga dharura na malengo ya familia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Vidokezo zaidi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
